[Not only is it unfair practice, but "penny wise pound foolish" as the saying goes, to not pay the healthcare workers. They are the backbone of the response to combat infectious diseases. The poor global economic situation is going to exacerbate this problem just when the healthcare workers are needed most. - Mod.LK

